., <a href=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/Sine.html">sine</a> equals
 <a href=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/OppositeSide.html">opposite side<=
/a> over <a href=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/Hypotenuse.html">hypotenu=
